* phase-6 part-3c/finish: external references.  ENTREF/SYMREF/SEGREF declare
* SUBR/DATA/SEG as external entry/symbol/segment references -- their names go in
* the RNAM record and they get 0-based EREF/SREF/SEGREF entries.  Using one in an
* address field emits a RELOC naming the entry (OPNDTYP OPEREREF=2 / OPERSREF=3 /
* OPERSEGREF=6, OPERAND = the entry number); TRA START stays a section relocation.
       OUNAME REFTEST
       ENTREF SUBR
       SYMREF DATA
       SEGREF SEG
START  LDA   DATA
       ADA   SUBR
       STA   SEG
       TRA   START
       END   START
